body:
nit:
```cpp
BOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(foo, true);
BOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(bar, false);
// vs
BOOST_CHECK(foo);
BOOST_CHECK(!bar);
```

but the surrounding code is already using the former, so it is ok to leave it as it is.

